  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": null,
      "text": "AGS05-2.5GL is a 5-port 2.5 Gbps Ethernet switch with loop detection. This multi-gigabit unmanaged Ethernet switch is a plug and play device with enterprise-level quality features. As a cost-effective solution, it allows increasing network bandwidth by more than twice (from 1 to 2.5 Gbps), using existing Cat5e (or better) cabling infrastructure."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "text": "Thanks to highly reliable internal components, features like auto-negotiation, non-blocking 25 Gbps switching capacity, flow control and fanless case design, this device will be perfect choice for SMB or home users."
    }
